<db:title>Property Documentation</db:title>
<db:section xml:id="opacity-prop">
<db:title>opacity : qreal</db:title>
<db:para>This property holds the opacity of the effect.</db:para>
<db:para>The value should be in the range of 0.0 to 1.0, where 0.0 is fully transparent and 1.0 is fully opaque.</db:para>
<db:para>By default, the opacity is 0.7.</db:para>
